item.title: CVE-2020-5233|2024-08-04T08:22:09.082Z -- pusher -- oauth2%20proxy
item.description: OAuth2 Proxy before 5.0 has an open redirect vulnerability. Authentication tokens could be silently harvested by an attacker. This has been patched in version 5.0.
